  "description": "A local-first Chrome extension that passively captures ChatGPT, Gemini, Claude, Grok, Perplexity conversations into a private memory graph. Features in-browser Hybrid RAG (Vector + BM25), semantic search, and 100% privacy via WebAssembly and IndexedDB. No servers, no API keys.",
